Version 0.2.1
-------------

- Fixed method :meth:`authorizeme.Authorization.rule`

Version 0.2
-----------

- Added ability to associate authorization rule with multiple classes at once.
- Added ability to associate authorization rule with nothing.
- Added ability to check multiple permissions at once.
- Changed parameters order of method :meth:`authorizeme.Authorization.add_rule`

